**Summary:** This documentation describes the Session Replay wrapper integration for Rudderstack, detailing how to install the @amplitude/session-replay-browser package and configure it to work with Rudderstack's Cloud-mode by mapping Rudderstack Anonymous ID to Amplitude Device ID and injecting sessionReplayProperties into track/page events.

